quran[14{c,v,t}:
18,84,hum ne is ko zameen mein Iqtidaar ataa kar rakha tha aur usay har qisam ke asbaab o wasail bakhshay thay
18,85,is ne ( pehlay maghrib ki taraf aik muhim ka ) sir o samaan kya
18,86,"hatta ke jab woh ghuroob aftaab ki had taq poanch gaya to is ne Sooraj ko aik kalay pani mein doubtey dekha aur wahan ussay aik qoum mili hum ne kaha"" ae zwalqrnin, tujhe yeh mqdrt bhi haasil hai ke un ko takleef pohnnchaye aur yeh bhi ke inn ke sath naik royih ikhtiyar kere """
18,87,"is ne kaha,"" jo un mein se zulm kere ga hum is ko saza den ge, phir woh apne rab ki taraf pultaya jaye ga aur woh usay aur ziyada sakht azaab day ga"
18,88,"aur jo un mein se imaan laaye ga aur naik amal kere ga uss ke liye achi jaza hai aur hum is ko naram ehkaam den ge """
18,89,phir uss ne ( aik doosri muhim ki ) tayari ki
18,90,yahan taq ke Tulu aftaab ki hadd taq ja pouncha wahan is ne dekha ke Sooraj aik aisi qoum par tulu ho raha hai jis ke liye dhoop se bachney ka koi samaan hum ne nahi kya hai
18,91,"yeh haal tha unn ka, aur zwalqrnin ke paas jo kuch tha ussay hum jantay thay"
18,92,phir is ne ( aik aur muhim ka ) samaan kya
18,93,yahan taq ke jab do pahoron ke darmain pouncha to usay un ke paas aik qoum mili jo mushkil hi se koi baat samjhti thi
18,94,"unn logon ne kaha ke"" ae zwalqrnin, yajooj aur majooj is sarzamen mein fasaad pheilatay hain to kya hum tujhe koi tax is kaam ke liye den ke to hamaray aur un ke darmain aik band taamer kar day? """
18,95,"is ne kaha"" jo kuch mere rab ne mujhe day rakha hai woh bohat hai tum bas mehnat se meri madad karo, mein tumahray aur un ke darmain band banaye deta hon"
18,96,"mujhe lohay ki chadrin laa kar do"" aakhir jab dono pahoron ke darmiyani khalaa ko is ne paat diya to logon se kaha ke ab aag dehka-o hatta ke jab ( yeh aahinii deewar ) bilkul aag ki terhan surKh ho gayi to is ne kaha"" lao, ab mein is par pighla howa tanba اundaylon ga """
18,97,( yeh band aisa tha ke ) yajooj o majooj is par charh kar bhi nah aa satke thay aur is mein naqb lagana un ke liye aur bhi mushkil tha
